# 7. Career Strategy

## 7.1 Answer to the Research Question

> **AI career growth is strongest in innovation-intensive states and metros** — California, Virginia, Washington, Massachusetts, New York, and the DC area — with San Francisco, San Jose, Seattle, and Boston leading at the metro level. **Broader non-AI job growth is strongest in Sun Belt labor markets** — especially Florida and Texas — with Dallas–Fort Worth and Austin among the most prominent metros. **Texas stands out as the only state performing strongly on both dimensions.**

